{"tid":2305128,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華期望向大陸影人學習 被央視女主持攔截邀跳舞","createTime":"2020-11-29T11:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T11:48:29.000Z","uid":183058,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e44b8bd9451b989926eb0795605518c1c39ee6f","tid":2305128,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T11:14:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201128/JGOTEH2BLJEC3F5YD2GUWZNTIE/?fbclid=IwAR1Y_8KRq9b7tYafA5yV9jpVH8L0IFGQ1VSPKNxxS7AihuptSIb1PqBjLig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201128%2FJGOTEH2BLJEC3F5YD2GUWZNTIE%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Y_8KRq9b7tYafA5yV9jpVH8L0IFGQ1VSPKNxxS7AihuptSIb1PqBjLig&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGic22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=bc3b5317\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201128%2FJGOTEH2BLJEC3F5YD2GUWZNTIE%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Y_8KRq9b7tYafA5yV9jpVH8L0IFGQ1VSPKNxxS7AihuptSIb1PqBjLig&h=cc70da3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201128/JGOTEH2BLJEC3F5YD2GUWZNTIE/?fbclid=IwAR1Y_8KRq9b7tYafA5yV9jpVH8L0IFGQ1VSPKNxxS7AihuptSIb1PqBjLig</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JwzheMebzfP6IY1JTV4oeYZK5s0=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MMQYCADVUNDAFFSO7AO6UGAZZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJwzheMebzfP6IY1JTV4oeYZK5s0%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMMQYCADVUNDAFFSO7AO6UGAZZI.jpg&h=9ac88212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第33屆金雞獎頒獎禮今日在廈門舉行，去年為了與台灣金馬獎打對台，金雞獎選擇在同日舉行，事隔一年，金雞獎今年選擇在金馬獎頒獎禮後一星期舉行。去年藝人休息室因以藍白凳加淡黃色綢緞，搞到被一眾大陸網民嘲笑似靈堂，今年亦依然維持這種佈置。<br />\n<br />\n紅地毯於晚上6點舉行，中港台藝人各自有代表，分別見到謝霆鋒、劉德華、成龍、黃曉明、王大陸及歐陽娜娜等都先後出現。由曾國祥執導的《少年的你》獲得11項提名，他帶領主角易烊千璽及周冬雨等一同進場，而一身黑色西裝襯煲呔的劉德華，則與其監製的電影《人潮洶湧》劇組一同行紅地毯，其間華仔表現得相當興奮，事後華仔在接受央視訪問時，表示希望以後可以與大陸的電影人有更多交流：「我希望在未來可以跟這個行列的朋友交流，因為我是在香港長大，我們的電影還是跟這邊的題材、手法有一些不一樣，希望多跟他們學習，也希望能夠把我們以前跑過的路講一遍給他們聽。」之後當女主持要求華仔跳電影中的舞步時，最初表現尷尬的他最後亦答應，更拉着該主持一齊跳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成龍2次「了不起」來讚大陸<br />\n<br />\n至於成龍之前在金雞獎開幕式時受訪，他指2020年是不平凡的一年：「對全世界的電影人來說都不容易，但是我們中國電影人抱團在一起，讓我們成為世界第一個影院恢復營業、電影恢復生產的國家。」而成龍更講了2次「了不起」來讚大陸電影人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2UpZ6Q93D3nqqTJzOVRzqmdmgBQ=/1435x804/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ET2SX63CUJFO3GHKDPUK6TKPMY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2UpZ6Q93D3nqqTJzOVRzqmdmgBQ%3D%2F1435x804%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FET2SX63CUJFO3GHKDPUK6TKPMY.JPG&h=364f7161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_RP9GakbtNL2swIEGsiCj2Bp1VI=/1420x794/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VB7J4BZGSBCNLBHPUI2K5AI3AA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_RP9GakbtNL2swIEGsiCj2Bp1VI%3D%2F1420x794%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVB7J4BZGSBCNLBHPUI2K5AI3AA.JPG&h=304142dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WCWgixXC1aXwBlqjVOKMAo8JJfk=/1422x799/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQVJ4RX3SJCF5NGFDFZ2Q5WAAM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWCWgixXC1aXwBlqjVOKMAo8JJfk%3D%2F1422x799%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQVJ4RX3SJCF5NGFDFZ2Q5WAAM.JPG&h=9b416e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Z_eW_mP8Qauo0l4MCBQkTORpnrQ=/580x338/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/